File: templates/base.html
Purpose: Base template with dark theme and sidebar navigation
Created: 2024-09-13
Author: iambilky

Revision History:
- v1.0.0: Initial creation with dark theme
- v1.0.1: Added sidebar navigation and quick stats
- v1.0.2: Integrated data centers link
- v1.1.0: Added PDU/Power management link
- v1.2.0: Added IPAM (IP Address Management) link
